title: I-Fluid
notes: Doesn't support 1080p. The camera is controlled by the mouse, and sometimes I just can't move the camera anymore when I move the mouse to the right. Large framerate drops when the "fireworks" go off at the end of a level. I still marked it as "Completely Stable" because this is all probably exactly how it works on Windows too, judging by the feedback this game gets on the Steam forums.
